

1-   compile 'com.github.bumptech.glide:glide:3.7.0'

2-  Create Normal ImageView this write this line
    Glide.with(this).load(img_url).placeholder(image while loading)
    .error(image when error).into(img_view)

3- if load Gif file from project use this :

   GlideDrawableImageViewTarget imageViewTarget = new
                  GlideDrawableImageViewTarget(img_view);

   then load gif into imageViewTarget like this

   Glide.with(this).load(R.drawable.test_gif).into(imageViewTarget);

